body:
myonlypen replied to your post: Fun R/B/Y discovery of the day

Can you catch ghost marowaks on other floors if you don’t have the silph scope?

When you don’t have the Silph Scope, they’re all unidentified ghosts, which is another special case - they too will dodge any ball.
